author: Swagata Dam
title: Here Are Some Photos Of The Khans Chilling In Maldives
text:
Swagata Dam Mar . 31 . 2017 
The entire Khan daan is currently in Maldives to celebrate Arpita Khan and Ayush Sharma ‘s baby boy Ahil ‘s birthday. We’ve already shared many photos from the grand event (you can check them out here ). Now, here are some more picture of the Khans and the Arora sisters, Malaika and Amrita . A post shared by sohail khan (@sohailkhanofficial) on Mar 30, 2017 at 4:32am PDT A post shared by sohail khan (@sohailkhanofficial) on Mar 30, 2017 at 4:15am PDT A post shared by Amrita Arora (@amuaroraofficial) on Mar 30, 2017 at 7:03am PDT A post shared by Amrita Arora (@amuaroraofficial) on Mar 30, 2017 at 6:12am PDT 
And here’s the birthday boy’s father with his family. A post shared by Aayush Sharma (@aaysharma) on Mar 30, 2017 at 2:58am PDT 
Good times!
